Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己清楚你该做什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  治愈受伤的心  让金平糖变多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花儿闪着朝露的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早起的鸟儿有虫吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是以散步的心情偷懒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有条漂亮的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为绿叶…很美？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿叶很美就会惹人落泪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不太明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你是哪位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生  你要装成布娃娃才行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀是天界的琥珀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得我感觉你和普通人的气息不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这家伙面前无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生  好像在哪儿听过这名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有的吧  不是猪尾吕义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是和那很像的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是那个五百袛先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是知道名字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位五百袛先生原来样子这么可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个样子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  在这边我姑且用的是猪尾吕义这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  是猪尾吕义先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你是小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阳光变强之前  必须给庭院里的树浇水才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看树叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么看  也不会掉眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道  但是我一看树叶就会哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮忙的家伙是一个懒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是把这些树叶打扫干净  就要花一整天的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这里我就会忍不住流泪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我转眼间搞定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你笨手笨脚的  我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道琥珀小姐落泪的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她受伤了  我想治愈她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你看那种书也不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（书名：美味佳肴）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  说不定能找到某种提示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  干脆明天早起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去问琥珀小姐一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过头啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这种结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是琥珀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:07:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么不知趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你现在过去  明显就是一个电灯泡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着特地在半路上接我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里等我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以像这样和琇一郎先生一起回家  真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…我想多在你的身边待一会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这么卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种的你一辈子都不会有机会住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  这里没你的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算有钱  心灵也还是会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里学来这鬼知识的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从便利店的杂志上学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候进去打招呼比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能遵守约定  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琇一郎先生才是  熬夜工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…患者比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  这里果然没你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住在水中的精灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回应我的呼唤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我滋润树木的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救其生命而聚集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩惠之雨啊  倾盆而降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠小姐…猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都湿透啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我才是  擅自闯进来真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我看到了和一位男性在一起的琥珀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  跟踪了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我还是不明白琥珀小姐为什么会落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对此十分在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  每当看到美丽的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会想「啊  好想让琇一郎先生也看看啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中浮现出他的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起琇一郎先生时…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起后？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一紧  胸口附近就疼了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一紧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中朦朦胧胧的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在琇一郎先生身边时  心中满足的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔看到的  琇一郎先生那害羞的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这许许多多的事情装满了我的心  令人忍不住去回想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…眼泪就流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没办法很好地说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  不就是恋爱了于是很难受  所以就流泪了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  恋爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是恋爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就没懂  装什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的话烦恼也会随之而来  我在杂志上读到过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀小姐  你有什么烦恼的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是烦恼  就是琇一郎先生一直都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会这样的事情一次都没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是和喜欢的人一起去游乐园之类的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在游乐园约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧  琥珀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠会加油的
Comment: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:19.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和琇一郎先生在游乐园约会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀小姐的心就会被治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先必须对游乐园做下调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是游乐园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很愉快的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门票三千日元！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游乐园还要花钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  治愈琥珀这件事本身就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一等奖  夏威夷旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二等奖  温泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三等奖  游乐园门票
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗啦哗啦转过之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以掉出来的珠子的颜色来决定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖品全都是成对抽出的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  抽奖了  抽奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  那里好像在送游乐园的门票当礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  抽奖券呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有抽奖券的话是不能抽奖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拿游乐园的门票之前还需要抽奖券吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽奖券…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算…算了  一直沮丧下去也不是办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底琥珀她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽奖券  不太容易发现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你不是很失望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  再说哪会有那么巧掉在地上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抽奖券
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是抽奖券
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托让我转下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园门票
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜  中大奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五等奖  鳄鱼玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好疼爱它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西拿了只会碍事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得别人亲切地给我的  拒绝的话也太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是游乐园的话是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在送报纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  从清花老师那里听说你做的是批萨的打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批萨的打工我也在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抽奖得到的鳄鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…鳄鱼是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园的门票
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打工的地方得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把这门票让给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么能用这个鳄鱼交换吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀小姐要在游乐园约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个去和琇一郎先生约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些报纸是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在帮忙送报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到那些门票  在送报纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  但是我不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为琇一郎先生很忙  我想是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  好不容易得到的门票又不能浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小鸠你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和猪尾吕义先生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和猪尾吕义先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许想象！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不是琥珀小姐和琇一郎先生去的话就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想大概还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  任性的话我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是任性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和琥珀小姐在一起的琇一郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来是非常开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像琥珀小姐为琇一郎先生着想一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琇一郎先生应该也非常重视琥珀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想琇一郎先生一定也很想约会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琇一郎先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些门票  我可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琇一郎先生  可以和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不讨厌摩天轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见琥珀小姐他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天界来的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天界？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说时间限制？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在季节交替四次之前把瓶子装满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  说是有时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季节交替四次…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  让我们一年之内把瓶子装满
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有收集满的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去不了想去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  瓶子里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有增加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀小姐的心没能被治愈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就幸福满满的家伙根本就没有治愈的必要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说她没有受伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是该高兴的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负…100分？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人选失误  连这种事都不懂的家伙这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是  幸福满满的话我觉得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得那么悠闲  一年啊一年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我紧张点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又一副嘻嘻哈哈的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了要紧张点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张的表情是什么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的表情…谁做得出来啊！
